e Italy.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 652, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 646, \"end\": 651, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"score\": 0.5981413070747824, \"rank\": 0.6717810911031132, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_rugby_union_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the duo\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 504}, {\"ngram\": \"a time\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"6:10.99\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"back\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"goldsin\", \"from\": 556, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"a dominant display\", \"from\": 573, \"to\": 591}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Meanwhile, McCarthy joins his crew-mate in the elite club of Irish competitors to win a medal at more than one Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 781, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.8343526472395112, \"rank\": 0.19446214573867313, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\"}, {\"begin\": 717, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"score\": 0.8572664289478968, \"rank\": 0.1643650698315507, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Irish_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his crew-mate\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 695}, {\"ngram\": \"the elite club\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 713}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 742, \"to\": 749}, {\"ngram\": \"more than one Olympic Games\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 780}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 27-year-old is the fifth person to join the list and the second just this week after boxer Kellie Harrington also guaranteed at least a bronze in the 60kg category she won in Tokyo.\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 968, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kellie Harrington\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kellie_Harrington\"}, {\"begin\": 962, \"end\": 967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9997351122019426, \"rank\": 0.0002649579555576729, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fifth person\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 818}, {\"ngram\": \"the list\", \"from\": 827, \"to\": 835}, {\"ngram\": \"at least a bronze\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"the 60kg category\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 950}]}, {\"sentence\": \"O'Donovan (30) won the first of his three medals alongside brother Gary at Rio 2016, where they took silver.\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 1078, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"O'Donovan\", \"from\": 970, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"his three medals\", \"from\": 1002, \"to\": 1018}, {\"ngram\": \"brother Gary\", \"from\": 1029, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio 2016\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1053}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1077}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He was then partnered with McCarthy and they went on to win gold at the Covid-19 pandemic-delayed Tokyo Games in 2021.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1107, \"end\": 1115, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"score\": 0.8343526472395112, \"rank\": 0.19446214573867313, \"text\": \"McCarthy\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon_McCarthy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brandon